name: Unidentified_Weequay_bounty_hunter
content:
A Weequay bounty hunter was active in 21 BBY, during the Clone Wars.
This bounty hunter was present along with another bounty hunter, a fellow Weequay, and two Humans, also bounty hunters, in Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina on Tatooine. They were scrolling through a list of the latest bounties when they came across the Nightbrother Savage Opress and decided to take him, since he was worth the most credits. Asajj Ventress stepped in, however; and said that this one was for her.
This Weequay wore goggles and protective armor.
